FBIS3-19285 "drweu050_q_94008" FBIS-WEU-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 TURKEY Firebomb Hits True Path Party Office in Mersin TA1503110494 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 0930 GMT 15 Mar 94 TA1503110494 Ankara ANATOLIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Mersin, March 15 (AA) -- Unidentified people threw a firebomb at the ruling major coalition True Path Party (DYP) party's election office in southern Mersin Province, it was reported on Monday [14 March]. Two people were wounded in the fire that erupted after the blast. AA reporter was told that the incident took place in the afternoon and the fire was extinguished by neighbors. An investigation was started, police said.
